<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 9px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 28px 0;
      min-height: 100%;
    }
    .page-inner {
      max-width: 170mm;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .section {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5px;
    }
    .full-width {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
    .inline-label {
      font-weight: bold;
      display: inline;
    }
    .three-cols {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5px;
    }
    .table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .table td {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 3px;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    .signature-section {
      margin-top: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 7px;
    }
    .bottom-info {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 5px;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .bold {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .small {
      font-size: 7px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-inner">
  <div class="header">BILL OF LADING</div>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">SHIPPER/EXPORTER (COMPLETE NAME, ADDRESS, PHONE/FAX AND CNPJ)</div>
      <div><%= shipperName %></div>
      <div><%= shipperAddress %></div>
      <div>CNPJ: <%= shipperCnpj %></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">CONSIGNEE (COMPLETE NAME, ADDRESS, PHONE/FAX)</div>
      <div><%= consigneeName %></div>
      <div><%= consigneeAddress %></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">NOTIFY PARTY (COMPLETE NAME, ADDRESS, PHONE/FAX AT DESTINATION)</div>
      <div>SAME AS CONSIGNEE</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">FORWARDING AGENT (REFERENCES)</div>
      <div><%= brazilBiName %></div>
      <div><%= brazilBiAddress %></div>
      <div>CNPJ: <%= brazilBiCnpj %></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="three-cols">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">BOOKING NO.</div>
      <div><%= bookingNo %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">B/L NO.</div>
      <div><%= blNumber %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">NUMBER ORIGIN</div>
      <div>THREE (3)</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">PRE-CARRIAGE BY</div>
      <div>&nbsp;</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">PLACE OF RECEIPT</div>
      <div><%= placeOfReceipt %></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">POINT AND COUNTRY OF ORIGIN (For the Merchant's Reference only)</div>
    <div>&nbsp;</div>
  </div>

  <div class="three-cols">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">VESSEL / VOYAGE</div>
      <div><%= vessel %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">PORT OF LOADING</div>
      <div><%= portOfLoading %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">EXCESS LIMIT DECLARATION AS PER CLAUSE 15:</div>
      <div>&nbsp;</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="three-cols">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">PORT OF DISCHARGE</div>
      <div><%= portOfDischarge %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">PLACE OF DELIVERY</div>
      <div><%= placeOfDelivery || '&nbsp;' %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">ONWARD INLAND ROUTE</div>
      <div>&nbsp;</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">MARKS & NOS / NO. OF PKGS / SHIPPER'S DESCRIPTION OF PACKAGES AND GOODS</div>
    <div style="margin-top: 5px;">
      <div class="bold">PARTICULARS FURNISHED BY SHIPPER</div>
      <div style="margin-top: 3px;">
        <div><%= containers %></div>
        <div style="margin-top: 3px;"><%= containerType %></div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 5px;">
        <div><%= packages %> OF <%= description %></div>
        <div>NCM: <%= ncm %></div>
        <div>NET WT: <%= netWeight %> KGS</div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 5px;">
        <div class="bold">SHIPPER'S LOAD AND COUNT AND SEAL</div>
        <div>WE DECLARE THAT NO WOODEN MATERIAL IS INCLUDED</div>
        <div>IN THIS CONTAINER OR CONTAINERS SHIPPED UNDER THIS DOCUMENT</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">GROSS WEIGHT</div>
      <div><%= grossWeight %> KGS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">MEASUREMENT</div>
      <div><%= measurement %> CBM</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <table class="table">
    <tr>
      <td style="width: 20%;"><span class="bold">ITEM NO.</span></td>
      <td style="width: 30%;"><span class="bold">FREIGHT RATES</span></td>
      <td style="width: 25%;"><span class="bold">CHARGES PREPAID</span></td>
      <td style="width: 25%;"><span class="bold">COLLECT</span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>FREIGHT</td>
      <td>&nbsp;</td>
      <td><%= currency %> <%= freightValue %></td>
      <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="2"><span class="bold">TOTAL</span></td>
      <td><span class="bold"><%= currency %> <%= freightValue %></span></td>
      <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="4"><span class="bold">PAYABLE AT</span></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="bottom-info">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">PLACE AND DATE OF ISSUE</div>
      <div><%= issueDate %></div>
      <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
        <div class="bold">SHIPPED ON BOARD DATE:</div>
        <div><%= shippedOnBoardDate %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">STAMP / SIGNATURE OF THE CARRIER OR ITS AGENT</div>
      <div style="height: 40px;">&nbsp;</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="signature-section">
    <div class="bold">RECEIVED</div> by the Carrier the Goods as specified above in apparent good order and condition unless otherwise stated, to be transported to such place as agreed, authorized or permitted herein and subject to all the terms and conditions appearing on the front and reverse of this Bill of Lading to which the Merchant agrees by accepting this Bill of Lading, and local privileges and customs notwithstanding. The particulars given above as stated by the shipper and the weight, measure, quantity, condition, contents and value of the Goods are unknown to the Carrier. In WITNESS whereof three (3) original Bills of Lading have been signed if not otherwise stated above, the same being accomplished the other(s), if any, to be void. If required by the Carrier one (1) original Bill of Lading must be surrendered duly endorsed in exchange for the Goods or delivery order.
  </div>

  <div class="section small" style="margin-top: 5px;">
    <div class="bold">JURISDICTION AND LAW CLAUSE</div>
    <div>The contract evidenced by or contracted in this Bill of Lading is governed by the Law of Hong Kong and any claim or dispute arising hereafter or in connection herewith shall be determined by the Courts in Hong Kong and no other Courts.</div>
  </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
